title: Michelle Childerley Chakra Balancing DVD
description:
The body's chakras or centres of energy ensure the flow of vital energy around the body to support the immune system and to promote well being and vibrant health.



Chakra Balancing empowers you with ancient knowledge of how the chakras work and will teach you 2 powerful energy techniques that will balance your chakras.



Follow Michelle Childerley as she explains in amazing detail how the chakra system works and shows you how to balance each chakra using the EFT emotional freedom technique and the Balance procedure.



This inspirational and 'easy-to-use' 8-part DVD shows you how to quickly balance the following chakras:

* Base Chakra
* Sacral Chakra
* Solar Plexus Chakra
* Heart Chakra
* Throat Chakra
* Third Eye Chakra
* Crown Chakra
* and much, much more

Realize your potential to feel good and balance your energy the easy way!
